|               |         SchemaCastScanExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |
|               |           CooperativeExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |
|               |             RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(3), input_partitions=1                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |
|               |               BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |
|               |                 CooperativeExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
